item.title: Error_game_js5io Help Please
item.dc:creator: @Spy2805 Spy2805
item.description:
@Spy2805 wrote:

Lots of people have this problem ok here is what you do:

1.Right click on the run file

2.Click edit

3.Change the jdk version to yours for example.

@echo off cd ../bin "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_01\bin\java.exe" palidino76/rs2/Server 43594 pause
To

@echo off cd ../bin "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\java.exe" palidino76/rs2/Server 43594 pause

4.Save it

5.double click the server

6.get the 508 ip_changer Run it

7.enter 0.0.0.0 for your ip

8.And log in
